data.description: *Agent related to Seller*  Introducing a beautiful two-story home in the well established Swim/Tennis community, Wild Meadows. This home has been completely renewed for its next owner. Inside, you are greeted by a two-story foyer and double French doors leading you into the Study. Enjoy high-end LVP light wood flooring throughout the main level and bathrooms as well as brand new carpet in the bedrooms, fresh interior paint, brand new appliances, and all new plumbing fixtures and toilets. The study would serve as a great office or playroom with double glass French doors, and double doors separating it from the dining room. The spacious dining room seating 12+ guests is the perfect space to entertain this holiday season! Situated at the back of the home is an open-concept kitchen and living room, with double glass doors that lead to the oversized screened porch. New details in the updated kitchen include new quartz countertops, tile backsplash, a large sink with a disposal, and new stainless steel and black appliances. Large living room with gas fireplace, and bracing to hang a large tv over the mantle. Once you move to the outside area you have the screened in porch with 2 patios, and a covered grill area. This home also features a very large fenced in backyard. Upstairs, enjoy a bonus room that separates the primary bedroom from the remaining guest rooms. You will fall in love with the spacious primary suite that features vaulted ceilings, a separate seating area with large closet, and an updated primary bathroom with dual sinks, a soaking tub and a brand new large tile shower. This home has been well maintained and includes tons of structural/system improvements and design enhancements. Wild Meadows is a fantastic, active community with easy access to 400.
